<task id="043" project="sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2">
  <metadata>
    <title>P4.D — Coverlet baseline measurement per project (no threshold enforcement)</title>
    <phase>Phase 4</phase>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <estimated-effort>2-4 hours</estimated-effort>
    <dependencies>039</dependencies>
    <blocks>080</blocks>
    <tags>phase-4, ci-cd, coverlet, coverage, measurement</tags>
    <rigor-hint>STANDARD</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Coverlet already active in CI (sdap-ci.yml lines 85-102 via config/coverlet.runsettings); task scope is measurement + baseline doc. Minimal CI change possible (no threshold add); no `src/` or test logic edits. STANDARD per CLAUDE.md §8.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>P4-W1</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Writes only to `projects/.../baseline/coverlet-baseline-2026-08-XX.md`. CI YAML touched IF needed (likely not — already wired). Disjoint write path from Track A (audits/), B (stryker-config.json + baseline/mutation-*), C (src/server Workspace + tests), E (baseline/anti-drift).</parallel-reason>
    <production-fix-per-ledger>false</production-fix-per-ledger>
    <repair-not-rewrite>false</repair-not-rewrite>
